<plot>Isabel thinks she has found the key to save the world from global warming and the energy crisis. Heavily equipped and accompanied by a technical consultant she travels to a glacier where her former professor is growing tomatoes on the material of the glaziers, the blue ice. What she did not think of is the nature of men, alone on the white and blue plains.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?406223</url></doc>
